lete this task directly. The `tavily_search` tool is not available in my subagent tool context - I only have access to: read, write, edit, process, and image.\n\nThe process tool requires an existing sessionId for exec actions, but there are no running sessions available, and I cannot create new exec sessions.\n\n**To complete this search, the main agent should:**\n\n1. Run directly: `tavily_search(query=\"AI 人工智能 2026\", count=5, search_depth=\"basic\")`\n\n2. Or via CLI: `node ~/.openclaw/extensions/openclaw-tavily/scripts/search.mjs \"AI 人工智能 2026\" -n 5`\n\n**Task status:** Blocked - missing tavily_search tool access in subagent context. The main agent has the necessary tool availability to execute this search."}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"dashscope-coding","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773504473911}}
